OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUK allows emergency use of 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbee-harming neonicotinoid  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fpesticide                  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The UK government has authorised the   
OL,6, emergency use of a type of pesticide   
OL,7, almost entirely banned in the EU       
OL,8, because of the harm it can cause bees. 
OL,10,FA Defra spokesperson said the use of   
OL,11,Fone type of neonicotinoid on sugar beet
OL,12,Fwas "based on robust scientific        
OL,13,Fassessment".                           
OL,15,FThe use would be subject to strict     
OL,16,Fconditions, Defra said.                
OL,18,FBut the Chief Executive of the Wildlife
OL,19,FTrusts, Craig Bennett, called it       
OL,20,F"scandalous".                          
